children: FastChain is being deprecated in favor of Lux.jl. Lux.jl uses functions with explicit parameters f(u,p) like FastChain, but is fully featured and documented machine learning library. See the Lux.jl documentation for more details.

StaticDense is being deprecated in favor of SimpleChains.jl. SimpleChain.jl is a non-allocating neural network library specialized to the small neural network cases. See its documentation for more details.
